{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"0c700589cd","title":"三幕话剧——官书记的“真理”","origin":"《关于“野草”、“蜜蜂”社反动小集团的材料》，中共中央民族学院整风办公室编，1957年12月。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"03995892d5","index":0,"year":1957,"month":5,"day":17,"articleId":"0c700589cd"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"01fcd89a36","name":"古林（刘金堂）"},{"id":"6dd61a6c39","name":"中央民族学院"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"c87c3df74e","type":"title","text":"三幕话剧——官书记的“真理”","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0c700589cd"},{"id":"ac20b41db2","type":"authors","text":"中央民族学院古林（刘金堂）","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0c700589cd"},{"id":"6cd7dc4f8c","type":"subtitle","text":"（刘金堂：中央民族学院语文系一年级藏语班学生）","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0c700589cd"},{"id":"d23e1fd372","type":"subtitle","text":"第一幕","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0c700589cd"},{"id":"7454e3d4e5","type":"paragraph","text":"人物：官书记，张某某。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0c700589cd"},{"id":"4b4701378f","type":"paragraph","text":"地点：某某楼走廊上。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0c700589cd"},{"id":"af8d29f97f","type":"paragraph","text":"(开幕)从走廊的一头传来了一阵令人酥麻的歌声，“郎呀!咱们俩是一条心……”随歌声，肥胖的某某官书记，晃荡着走上前场，一边仍然在低声的唱着那两句歌词。张××由后追上书记。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0c700589cd"},{"id":"be38764119","type":"paragraph","text":"张：书记同志?你好!","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0c700589cd"},{"id":"8970235065","type":"paragraph","text":"官：(停住脚，扭脸向上吹出一股长气)嗯!什么事儿?","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0c700589cd"},{"id":"d7ad6a5120","type":"paragraph","text":"张：自党中央号召“百花齐放、百家争鸣”以来各界人士为之活跃，而我们这里却仍然寂静无声。为了响应党的号召，活跃一下同学们的文娱生活，再者也想协助党的整风，所以，我们几个想办一个书刊……","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0c700589cd"},{"id":"21b646ef15","type":"paragraph","text":"官：(吃惊)什么?辨刊?","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0c700589cd"},{"id":"a270baf9ff","type":"paragraph","text":"张：是这样的书记同志!","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0c700589cd"},{"id":"9482b996be","type":"paragraph","text":"官：(沉思后)嗯!出版自由，乃宪法规定，“百家争鸣”是我党号召!没人敢于干涉……不过，凡事要三思而后行，你们几个人，又都是非党非团同学，谁敢保证以后不出差错!如果万一出了问题，责任可不轻；以我个人的意见，不如不出为好!民主纵然应该，但是也得有个限度呀!","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0c700589cd"},{"id":"b7067ab026","type":"paragraph","text":"张：我们只是活跃一下同学们的文娱生活，这不会有什么反动动机!请你相信……","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0c700589cd"},{"id":"0a2390d43d","type":"paragraph","text":"官：相信?!这不是说说了事的事呀!这就是我的意见。你要再仔细的考虑考虑!嗯?“郎呀!咱们俩是一条心……”","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0c700589cd"},{"id":"6257231faf","type":"paragraph","text":"(张呆于前场)","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0c700589cd"},{"id":"44e0d54829","type":"paragraph","text":"——幕落——","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0c700589cd"},{"id":"13d7e945b4","type":"subtitle","text":"第二幕","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0c700589cd"},{"id":"142c0e6ea1","type":"paragraph","text":"人物：官书记、张××。","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0c700589cd"},{"id":"e615893feb","type":"paragraph","text":"地点：官书记宿舍。","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0c700589cd"},{"id":"ea9502d355","type":"paragraph","text":"(开幕了)官、张相对而坐，双方都面红耳赤。","index":20,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0c700589cd"},{"id":"b9e1d11fe4","type":"paragraph","text":"张：既然你真不同意，那么就这样吧!不过刊物我们是一定要出的!","index":21,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0c700589cd"},{"id":"2fd57bc2b1","type":"paragraph","text":"官：(拍桌大怒而起)你出!你出!!你们这一群落后分子!你们知道我不能以行政的名义处分你们！我警告你们：我会命令我支部的全体团员，不许给你们写稿，不许看你们的文章!让你那个嗅刊在墙角起去鸣吧!","index":22,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0c700589cd"},{"id":"1a9f6acd61","type":"paragraph","text":"张：放心吧!书记同志，会有人支持它的!","index":23,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0c700589cd"},{"id":"0e4c607189","type":"paragraph","text":"官：呸!永远也不会有人支持你们的!我是党员，我是团支部书记，我不能眼看着在我们这里长出“毒草”，有人在这里散播反动言论!为“真理”为“正义”而奋斗，这是我的崇高的职责!","index":24,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0c700589cd"},{"id":"76b715951e","type":"paragraph","text":"张：(气愤而出)我相信你书记同志!你是一个为“真理”为“正义”而奋斗的“伟大战士”!你会因此而得到“光荣”的!","index":25,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0c700589cd"},{"id":"bb912fac24","type":"paragraph","text":"官：(气的将倒。大呼!)我要为“真理”献出我的一切!","index":26,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0c700589cd"},{"id":"5e918958a0","type":"paragraph","text":"——幕落——","index":27,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0c700589cd"},{"id":"dbe92b63af","type":"subtitle","text":"第三幕","index":28,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0c700589cd"},{"id":"bcbd35fb50","type":"paragraph","text":"人物：官书记、学生甲、乙、丙、丁……","index":29,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0c700589cd"},{"id":"16e59f747d","type":"paragraph","text":"地点：××楼进口处以内。","index":30,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0c700589cd"},{"id":"b2c3f72cc3","type":"paragraph","text":"(开幕)一群学生正围在一个新出的刊物前热烈的议论着，远处走廊的一端传来官书记的唱声：“郎呀!咱们俩是一条心……”慢慢的走近前台中央，在人群一边停下了。","index":31,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0c700589cd"},{"id":"70a80c0763","type":"paragraph","text":"官：喂!同志们这是什么布告呀!","index":32,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0c700589cd"},{"id":"d0da15c60e","type":"paragraph","text":"(群众闪开齐看官)","index":33,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0c700589cd"},{"id":"2c256ed571","type":"paragraph","text":"学生甲：是新出的墙报!书记同志!","index":34,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0c700589cd"},{"id":"2d98349768","type":"paragraph","text":"官：(大惊而后怒)呀!","index":35,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0c700589cd"},{"id":"1428c5eb03","type":"paragraph","text":"学生乙：办的不错呀!书记同志!你看这首诗，对那些浪费粮食的人狠狠的讽刺了一顿。","index":36,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0c700589cd"},{"id":"91b321b0a7","type":"paragraph","text":"学生丙：这篇小说写的是我们的义务劳动!真好!","index":37,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0c700589cd"},{"id":"e06388fda1","type":"paragraph","text":"官：(上气不接下气)什么？！胡说!你们都是瞎子!这是“毒草”，这是反动宣传!快——快!给我把它撤了!","index":38,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0c700589cd"},{"id":"b65005bb92","type":"paragraph","text":"学生丁：书记同志?你没有喝酒吧！","index":39,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0c700589cd"},{"id":"8def5fac48","type":"paragraph","text":"官：给我撤!撤呀!……","index":40,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0c700589cd"},{"id":"85a4fe39d5","type":"paragraph","text":"(没人动)","index":41,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0c700589cd"},{"id":"8efdc37b45","type":"appellation","text":"官：你们?要——","index":42,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0c700589cd"},{"id":"920ce99998","type":"paragraph","text":"(官想亲自下手，被学生们的怒目斥退，一阵笑声。)","index":43,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0c700589cd"},{"id":"7748cf5a22","type":"appellation","text":"官：你们?要——要干……什么？！","index":44,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0c700589cd"},{"id":"22f1bab713","type":"paragraph","text":"群众：不许碰它！","index":45,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0c700589cd"},{"id":"e26a46c738","type":"paragraph","text":"学生甲：官僚主义!","index":46,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0c700589cd"},{"id":"2af28173ad","type":"paragraph","text":"群众：(跟随着)官僚主义!","index":47,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0c700589cd"},{"id":"335aa6d2d8","type":"paragraph","text":"官狼狈后退至台口处又回头，手握拳头大呼!“毒草”!“毒草”！！！呵……我会……叫你们吃到苦头的！……","index":48,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0c700589cd"},{"id":"0712ba753f","type":"paragraph","text":"(一阵笑声)","index":49,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0c700589cd"},{"id":"543ec22624","type":"paragraph","text":"——幕落——","index":50,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0c700589cd"},{"id":"5f0a2210fd","type":"paragraph","text":" (录自“野草”第2期)","index":51,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0c700589cd"}],"page":{"id":"6bca8abc60","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0c700589cd","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}